Subject: Codex LM Studio Orchestration Workspace

Description: Canonical workspace contract for Codex-authored SOP context streams, LM Studio manager proposals, and gated OpenAI Codex CLI worker jobs.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_codex_lmstudio_orchestration_workspace\Dictated_Codex_LMStudio_Orchestration_Workspace_Source.sop
